ily: \'Comic Sans MS\'; font-size: large;\">CONTAMOS CON:</span></b></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\"><span size=\"2\" face=\"Verdana\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Verdana; font-size: small;\">L&aacute;ser transd&eacute;rmico (para ara&ntilde;as vasculares y v&aacute;rices).</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\"><span size=\"2\" face=\"Verdana\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Verdana; font-size: small;\">Cirug&iacute;a L&aacute;ser endominal (para venas grandes).</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\"><span size=\"2\" face=\"Verdana\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Verdana; font-size: small;\">Microcirug&iacute;a y Escleroterapia (venas de mediano calibre).</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\"><span size=\"2\" face=\"Verdana\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Verdana; font-size: small;\">L&aacute;ser para depilaci&oacute;n permanente.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><span size=\"2\" face=\"Verdana\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Verdana; font-size: small;\">Como resultados de v&aacute;lvulas defectuosas en las venas se forman protuberancias retorcidas que causan molestias y se ven antiest&eacute;ticas.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\"><span size=\"4\" face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=\"#008080\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; color: #008080; font-family: \'Comic Sans MS\'; font-size: large;\">&iquest;COMO SE ORIGINAN ESTOS PADECIMIENTOS?</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><span size=\"2\" face=\"Verdana\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Verdana; font-size: small;\">Como la sangre circula a trav&eacute;s de las venas hasta el coraz&oacute;n, se supone que las v&aacute;lvulas de contenci&oacute;n en las piernas previenen que la sangre fluya en direcci&oacute;n contraria, ya que por gravedad tiende a dirigirse hacia abajo.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><span size=\"2\" face=\"Verdana\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Verdana; font-size: small;\">Si las v&aacute;lvulas no se cierran correctamente, la sangre se estanca, forzando a las paredes de la vena a agrandarse y abultarse, as&iacute; se forman los diferentes padecimientos de las venas.</span></p>', 'https://www.facebook.com/venocentroelsalvador', 'http://www.venocentroelsalvador.com/', 'Aprobado', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\">85 Avenida Sur y Calle Cuscatlan #317</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\">Colonia Escal&oacute;n</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\">San Salvador</span></p>', '2264-9494', '2017-12-04 09:58:33', '2017-12-04 10:00:17');
