(15, 5, 20, 15, 'Clínica Dermalaser', '<div align=\"center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; font-weight: 300; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; color: #000000; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 0.1px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"></div>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; font-weight: 300; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style: disc; color: #000000; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 0.1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Depilaci&oacute;n permanente.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Eliminaci&oacute;n de Varices.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Eliminaci&oacute;n de nevos o lunares.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Celulitis.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Onococriptosis o u&ntilde;eros.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Tratamientos para el rostro:\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style: disc;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">IPL o Luz Pulsada Intensa.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Botox.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Materiales de relleno.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Faciales</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">En Cl&iacute;nica Dermalaser la satisfacci&oacute;n de nuestros pacientes es nuestro principal objetivo, por eso ofrecemos tratamientos efectivos realizados con la tecnolog&iacute;a m&aacute;s avanzada para: Depilaci&oacute;n permanente, eliminaci&oacute;n de celulitis, eliminaci&oacute;n de v&aacute;rices, eliminaci&oacute;n de lunares y mas&hellip;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Adem&aacute;s contamos con la experiencia del personal t&eacute;cnico capacitado en el uso de los equipos y la aplicaci&oacute;n de los tratamientos as&iacute; como el respaldo de m&eacute;dicos dermat&oacute;logos.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">D&eacute;janos consentirte y comparte esta experiencia en un ambiente agradable , exclusivo y seguro.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Vis&iacute;tanos&hellip; ser&aacute; un placer atenderte.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 40px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; font-weight: 500; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; line-height: 1.55em; color: #008080; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Quienes Somos</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">En noviembre 2003 nace CL&Iacute;NICA DERMALASER con un nuevo concepto para ofrecer servicios m&eacute;dicos relacionados a depilaci&oacute;n permanente con l&aacute;ser, eliminaci&oacute;n de v&aacute;rices con l&aacute;ser y escleroterapia, diagn&oacute;stico, eliminaci&oacute;n de lunares con radiofrecuencia y rejuvenecimiento facial entre otros. Todo en un ambiente agradable, moderno y confortable.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">CL&Iacute;NICA DERMALASER es atendida por m&eacute;dicos dermat&oacute;logos y especialistas en v&aacute;rices. Adem&aacute;s contamos con personal t&eacute;cnico femenino altamente capacitado en el uso de los equipos de depilaci&oacute;n y en la realizaci&oacute;n de los tratamientos faciales y corporales.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Contamos con tecnolog&iacute;a de punta para ofrecer soluciones a las diferentes necesidades de salud y belleza ofreciendo excelentes resultados.</p>', 'https://www.facebook.com/DermalaserSv', 'http://dermalaserelsalvador.com/', 'Aprobado', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\">Plaza Los Sue&ntilde;os</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\">2 nivel, locales 20 y 21&nbsp;</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\" mce-data-marked=\"1\">San Salvador</span></p>', '2306-1839', '2017-12-04 10:02:57', '2017-12-04 10:15:53'),
(16, 5, 18, 15, 'Centro Láser de Úlceras y Linfedermas', '<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 40px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; font-weight: 500; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; line-height: 1.55em; color: #008080; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Tipos de &uacute;lceras atendidas en Centro L&aacute;ser de &Uacute;lceras</h2>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">&Uacute;lceras por Presi&oacute;n</b><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\" />Son &aacute;reas de piel lesionadas por permanecer en una misma posici&oacute;n durante demasiado tiempo. Com&uacute;nmente se forman donde los huesos est&aacute;n m&aacute;s cercanos a la fiel, como los tobillos, los talones y las caderas.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\" />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">&Uacute;lceras Varicosas<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\" /></b>La ulcera varicosas es una complicaci&oacute;n severa de la mala circulaci&oacute;n venosa. Puede ser consecuencia de las varices, insuficiencia valvular superficial, safena, perforante o profunda. Producida por un deficiente funcionamiento del sistema venoso, generalmente en las piernas.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\" />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Pie Diab&eacute;tico</b><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\" />Trastorno de los pies de los diab&eacute;ticos provocado por la enfermedad de las arterias perif&eacute;ricas que irrigan el pie, complicado a menudo por da&ntilde;o a los nervios perif&eacute;ricos de pie e infecci&oacute;n. Debido a la oclusi&oacute;n de las arterias que llevan sangre a los pies se produce gangrena.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\" />El pie del paciente diab&eacute;tico es muy sensible a todas formas de traumatismo: el tal&oacute;n y las prominencias &oacute;seas resultan especialmente vulnerables.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 40px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; font-weight: 500; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; line-height: 1.55em; color: #008080; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Tratamientos</h2>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Plasma rico en plaquetas.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Ozonoterapia para &uacute;lceras.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Drenaje Linfatico Manual.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Vendaje comprensiovo para Linfedermas y Ulceras Venosas.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Vendaje Neuromuscular (Kinesloterapia).</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Rehabilitacion Pos Cirugia VenosA Y Ortopedica.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Reduccion de la marcha.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Ejercicio Terapeutico para el mejoramiento de la funcionalidad.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Manga de presion terapeutica a la medida.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Curacion con Ozono.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Curacion con Laser.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Fisioterapia.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Rehabilitacion Vascular periferica (unicos).</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Autphemo terapua Mayor.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Autohemo Terapia Menor.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Suero Ozonizado.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 40px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; font-weight: 500; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; line-height: 1.55em; color: #008080; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Enfermeras a Domicilio</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">La compa&ntilde;&iacute;a que env&iacute;a una enfermera para atender a usted o a su familiar las 24/7 los 365 d&iacute;as del a&ntilde;o.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Contamos con personal certificado que brinda un trato y atenci&oacute;n del primer nivel.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Brindamos atenci&oacute;n a:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Cuidados posteriores a cualquier cirug&iacute;a, incluyendo ces&aacute;rea y parto normal.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Discapacidades, limitaciones sensoriales (Alzaheimer, dificultades de visi&oacute;n y o&iacute;do).</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Enfermedades terminales y cuidados respiratorios.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Cuidados de adulto mayor.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Cuidado de ni&ntilde;os con capacidades especiales.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Curaciones y cuidados respiratorios.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Cuidados de bebe y ni&ntilde;os.</li>\r\n<li></li>\r\n</ul>', '<p align=\"center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://medicosdeelsalvador.com/imagenes/centro-laser-de-ulceras/logos2.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"118\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Avalado por la Escuela Colombiana de Linfolog&iacute;a en terapia f&iacute;sica para el manejo de linfedema. (Universidad Aut&oacute;noma de Bucaramanga).</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">El Centro L&aacute;ser de Ulceras le ofrecemos una completa gama de tratamientos profesionales que le garantizan la curaci&oacute;n y eliminaci&oacute;n total de todo tipo de ulceras.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Contamos con un staff de m&eacute;dicos especializados, que le atiende en todo el proceso de:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Consulta.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Operaci&oacute;n.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Convalecencia (curaci&oacute;n con apositos)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Las ventajas de nuestros tratamientos son:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Somos un centro que contamos contamos con sala de operaci&oacute;n propio y equipo especializado de &uacute;ltima generaci&oacute;n para el diagnostico de las enfermedades venosas ECO-DOPLER VASCULAR.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">En caso de ser necesario la cirug&iacute;a es completamente ambulatoria es decir se efect&uacute;a el un mismo d&iacute;a ya que contamos con un servicio integral donde le tomamos ex&aacute;menes d laboratorio, Doppler, evaluaci&oacute;n de riesgo cardiovascular-incluido electrocardiograma y curaci&oacute;n con ap&oacute;sitos. Si su caso lo requiere.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Oclusi&oacute;n permanente con Endol&aacute;ser para venas defectuosas, responsables de la ulcera.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Para el mejor tratamiento de su ULCERA utilizamos materiales especiales y adecuados para garantizarle se completa curaci&oacute;n:\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style: disc;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Ap&oacute;sitos</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">VAC Terapia de cicatrizaci&oacute;n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Injertos (si lo requiere el paciente).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Atenci&oacute;n post-operatoria que garantiza una completa eliminaci&oacute;n de ulceras, sin salir a otras instalaciones.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">El Centro L&aacute;ser de Ulceras le ofrecemos una completa gama de tratamientos profesionales que le garantizan la curaci&oacute;n y eliminaci&oacute;n total de todo tipo de ulceras<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\" />Las causas principales de ulceras son:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Diabetes (pie diabetico)</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Posici&oacute;n de dec&uacute;bito ( por permanecer acostado)</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Por quemaduras</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Por varices</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Por golpes</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Por estar mucho tiempo sentado en la silla de ruedas.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Si su problema no se encuentra en este listado, estamos seguros de poder ayudarle. Llame o escriba un e-mail describiendo brevemente su problema, con gusto le daremos una cita para evaluar su problema.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">La aplicaci&oacute;n&nbsp;<b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">laser por fototerapia</b>&nbsp;proporciona los siguientes efectos terap&eacute;uticos:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Efecto analg&eacute;sico: reduce la inflamaci&oacute;n, provocando la reabsorci&oacute;n de exudados, favoreciendo la eliminaci&oacute;n de sustancias al&oacute;genas.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Efecto antinflamatorio: interfiere en la s&iacute;ntesis de prostaglandinas determinando una reducci&oacute;n sensible en las alteraciones proporcionadas por la inflamaci&oacute;n.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Efecto antiedematoso: el est&iacute;mulo de la microcirculaci&oacute;n proporciona mejores condiciones para resolver la congesti&oacute;n ocasionada por el desborde de plasma que forma el edema.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Efecto cicatrizante: debido al aumento de la velocidad de formaci&oacute;n de nuevos vasos que generan mejores condiciones para una cicatrizaci&oacute;n m&aacute;s r&aacute;pida y est&eacute;ticamente significativa.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Indicaciones</b></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">El laser adem&aacute;s puede utilizarse para la fotobiomodulaci&oacute;n celular a trav&eacute;s de las aplicaciones de luz.</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Rejuvenecimiento.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Cicatrizaci&oacute;n.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Pre y postoperatorio.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Flacidez tisular.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Bactericida.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Procesos inflamatorios.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://www.facebook.com/centrolaserdeulceras', 'http://www.centrolasersv.com/', 'Aprobado', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\">Avenida Maracaibo #3017</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\">por colegio Garc&iacute;a Flamenco junto a Maya Caf&eacute;</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\">Colonia Miramonte</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\">San Salvador</span></p>', '2124-9300', '2017-12-04 10:03:53', '2017-12-04 10:15:45');
