-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Tecnolog&iacute;a de punta especializada en cirug&iacute;a laparosc&oacute;pica y ambulatoria, brindando a nuestros pacientes la m&aacute;xima eficiencia en cirug&iacute;as de corta estancia.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Contamos con Laboratorio Cl&iacute;nico propio, para brindar a nuestros pacientes mayor comodidad y rapidez en el resultado de sus an&aacute;lisis.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Precios accesibles y paquetes quir&uacute;rgicos altamente competitivos.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Convenios con las principales compa&ntilde;&iacute;as de seguros m&eacute;dicos del pa&iacute;s.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Abierto al gremio m&eacute;dico.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Se aceptan todas las tarjetas de cr&eacute;dito.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Ubicaci&oacute;n estrat&eacute;gica.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 40px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; font-weight: 500; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; line-height: 1.55em; color: #008080; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Beneficios de la Cirug&iacute;a de M&iacute;nima Invasi&oacute;n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">&iquest;Qu&eacute; es la cirug&iacute;a de m&iacute;nima invasi&oacute;n?</b></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Se refiere a t&eacute;cnicas quir&uacute;rgicas con abordajes m&iacute;nimos, es decir, cirug&iacute;as realizadas a trav&eacute;s de peque&ntilde;as incisiones, con un sistema de micro c&aacute;mara de alta resoluci&oacute;n.</p>\r\n<div align=\"center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"></div>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; font-weight: 300; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style: disc; color: #000000; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 0.1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Las incisiones son m&iacute;nimas, hasta 2 mil&iacute;metros.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Hay menos dolor.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Recuperaci&oacute;n temprana de la cirug&iacute;a.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Reducci&oacute;n de tiempo de hospitalizaci&oacute;n.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Integraci&oacute;n anticipada a las actividades cotidianas.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Mayor precisi&oacute;n en la realizaci&oacute;n de los procedimientos quir&uacute;rgicos.</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p align=\"center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://medicosdeelsalvador.com/imagenes/cecimi/logo-cecimi.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%;\" /></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 40px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; font-weight: 500; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; line-height: 1.55em; color: #008080; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Quienes Somos</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">El CENTRO DE CIRUG&Iacute;A DE MINIMA INVASI&Oacute;N ESCAL&Oacute;N (CECIMI)</b>, es el Centro especializado en Cirug&iacute;a Laparosc&oacute;pica Avanzada; conformado por un grupo de m&eacute;dicos cirujanos pioneros en el pa&iacute;s y con m&aacute;s de 15 a&ntilde;os de experiencia en las t&eacute;cnicas de laparoscop&iacute;a avanzada, utilizando las t&eacute;cnicas de la m&iacute;nima invasi&oacute;n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">El CECIMI est&aacute; enfocado en la realizaci&oacute;n de cirug&iacute;as de corta estancia y cirug&iacute;as especializadas en las t&eacute;cnicas de laparoscopia, como puede ser la extirpaci&oacute;n de la ves&iacute;cula, un ap&eacute;ndice o una resecci&oacute;n intestinal.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Su infraestructura ha sido dise&ntilde;ada especialmente para realizar cirug&iacute;as que reducen el trauma quir&uacute;rgico, buscando el equilibrio con un ambiente tranquilo y acogedor, facilitando la recuperaci&oacute;n del paciente despu&eacute;s de una intervenci&oacute;n quir&uacute;rgica.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Su misi&oacute;n, es la de prestar servicios de salud de corta estancia, especializados en cirug&iacute;as de m&iacute;nima invasi&oacute;n, de forma oportuna, efectiva y de calidez, aceptando el compromiso de ayudar a la comunidad.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Bienvenido a nuestra p&aacute;gina, le invitamos a que nos visite y conozca las ventajas que ofrece CECIMI; una excelente alternativa para la realizaci&oacute;n de sus cirug&iacute;as.</p>', 'http://www.facebook.com/pages/Cecimi/385253834853085', 'http://cecimi.com/', 'Aprobado', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\">Medicentro Escal&oacute;n</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\">9&ordf; calle pte. N&deg; 4729</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\">Colonia Escal&oacute;n</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px; background-color: #fafbfb;\">San Salvador</span></p>', '2263-8167', '2017-12-04 10:07:40', '2017-12-04 10:22:01');
