(21, 4, 27, 15, 'Clinicas y Opticas Candray', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Cirug&iacute;as Refractivas</b></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">LASIK: t&eacute;cnica que utiliza un Excimer L&aacute;ser para corregir la miop&iacute;a, astigmatismo y la hipermetrop&iacute;a. Ideal para pacientes entre los 20 a 40 a&ntilde;os.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Lentes f&aacute;quicos: lentes de implante intraocular de los fabricantes STAAR ICL y ALCON Cachet. Es la cirug&iacute;a necesaria para aquellos pacientes que no son candidatos para la cirug&iacute;a LASIK. Ideal para pacientes entre los 20 a 40 a&ntilde;os.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Cirug&iacute;a Facorefractiva: una alternativa para aquellos pacientes mayores de 40 a&ntilde;os que padecen de graduaciones muy altas.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Unidad de Glaucoma</b></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Campimetr&iacute;a, Tomograf&iacute;a del nervio &oacute;ptico (HRT), Paquimetr&iacute;a</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Tratamiento L&aacute;ser: iridotom&iacute;as y trabeculoplastia selectiva l&aacute;ser (SLT)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Unidad de Retina</b></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Angiograf&iacute;a Digital, fotograf&iacute;a de retina y nervio &oacute;ptico, tratamiento con l&aacute;ser arg&oacute;n para la retinopat&iacute;a diab&eacute;tica, inyecci&oacute;n de Avastin, Triamcinolona y Lucentis. Vitrectom&iacute;a con micro-incisi&oacute;n con equipo Constellation de alta tecnolog&iacute;a.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Unidad de Vias Lagrimales y Pl&aacute;stica Ocular</b></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Unidad de Estrabismo y Oftalmolog&iacute;a Pedi&aacute;trica</b></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Unidad de Enfermedades Externas:</b>&nbsp;Pterigi&oacute;n, ojo seco, ulceras corneales, conjuntivitis y otras patolog&iacute;as de la superficie ocular.</p>\r\n<p></p>', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Sucursal Central:</b>&nbsp;17 Calle Poniente y 1a Ave. Norte, No. 145, Barrio San Miguelito, San Salvador.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\" />Tel.: (503) 2233-6500</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Sucursal Escal&oacute;n:&nbsp;</b>91 Ave. Norte No. 446, Colonia Escal&oacute;n, San Salvador<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\" />Tel.: (503) 2263-2870</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Sucursal Santa Tecla:&nbsp;</b>Edificio Centro de Odontolog&iacute;a y Ciencias Integrales, 3er nivel, 7a. Av. Norte y 7a. Calle oriente #7, Colonia Santa Monica, Contiguo al Colegio Champagnat.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\" />Tel. 2233-6520.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Cl&iacute;nicas Candray fue fundada en 1945 por el Dr. Carlos Humberto Candray, como una cl&iacute;nica especializada en tratar las enfermedades de los ojos. A partir de su fundaci&oacute;n como empresa familiar, tres generaciones de m&eacute;dicos oftalm&oacute;logos han prestado sus servicios a los salvadore&ntilde;os de todas las edades y de varios puntos del pa&iacute;s.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Contamos con los siguientes oftalm&oacute;logos especialistas:</p>\r\n<div align=\"center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">\r\n<table border=\"1\" width=\"575\" cellspacing=\"3\" cellpadding=\"3\" bordercolor=\"#DEDEDE\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n<td align=\"center\" width=\"50%\" height=\"50\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; border-collapse: collapse;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://medicosdeelsalvador.com/doctor/ncandray\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: top; text-decoration-line: none; color: #026a9f; transition: color 0.4s ease, background-color 0.4s ease; outline: none !important;\">Dr. Napole&oacute;n Candray</a></b><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\" />(Director)</td>\r\n<td align=\"center\" width=\"50%\" height=\"50\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; border-collapse: collapse;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://medicosdeelsalvador.com/doctor/acandray\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: top; text-decoration-line: none; color: #026a9f; transition: color 0.4s ease, background-color 0.4s ease; outline: none !important;\">Dr. Alejandro Candray</a></b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n<td align=\"center\" width=\"50%\" height=\"50\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; border-collapse: collapse;\">Dra. Carmen Elena Candray</td>\r\n<td align=\"center\" width=\"50%\" height=\"50\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; border-collapse: collapse;\">Dr. Salvador Mena</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n<td align=\"center\" width=\"50%\" height=\"50\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; border-collapse: collapse;\">Dr. Edwin Arias</td>\r\n<td align=\"center\" width=\"50%\" height=\"50\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; border-collapse: collapse;\">Dr. Julio Mart&iacute; Candray</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n<td align=\"center\" width=\"50%\" height=\"50\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; border-collapse: collapse;\">Dr. Juan Ram&oacute;n Carbajal</td>\r\n<td align=\"center\" width=\"50%\" height=\"50\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; border-collapse: collapse;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">Cl&iacute;nicas Candray fue la pionera en introducir la cirug&iacute;a de catarata sin hospitalizaci&oacute;n. A partir de entonces, muchos salvadore&ntilde;os han confiado su salud ocular</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Contamos con los siguientes servicios:</b></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Unidad de Cirug&iacute;a de Catarata de Alta Tecnolog&iacute;a</b></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: #fafbfb; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">100% ambulatoria</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">T&eacute;cnica moderna de Facoemulsificaci&oacute;n, aspirando la catarata a trav&eacute;s de una microincisi&oacute;n de 2mm. Herida sin puntos, anestesia solo con gotas sin inyecciones.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Lentes intraoculares de la mejor calidad:\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style: disc;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Acrysof IQ: lente monofocal de alto dise&ntilde;o &oacute;ptico, permite excelente visi&oacute;n lejana, requiere el uso de anteojos para lectura.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Acrysof Toric: lente monofocal que corrige el astigmatismo preoperatorio, requiere el uso de anteojos de lectura.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Acrysof Restor: lente multifocal que permite visi&oacute;n lejana y cercana. Permite leer sin anteojos.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Acrysof Restor Toric: lente multifocal que corrige el astigmatismo preoperatorio.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">T&eacute;cnica SICS (Small Incision Cataract Surgery): cirug&iacute;a de extracci&oacute;n manual de la catarata, a trav&eacute;s de una incisi&oacute;n arquitect&oacute;nicamente mas respetuosa que la herida utilizada en la cirug&iacute;a extracapsular antigua. Permite costos accesibles con excelentes resultados.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Tecnolog&iacute;a Avanzada:\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style: disc;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Utilizamos equipos de fabricaci&oacute;n alemana, japonesa, suiza y americana. Todos ellos cumplen con los est&aacute;ndares internacionales actuales, permiti&eacute;ndonos ofrecer la misma tecnolog&iacute;a que en pa&iacute;ses desarrollados.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">IOL Master: permite calcular el lente intraocular con alta precisi&oacute;n, &uacute;nico en el pa&iacute;s.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Microscopio Especular: para detectar factores de riesgo de la c&oacute;rnea asociados a edad avanzada y cataratas muy maduras.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">Topograf&iacute;a Corneal: permite evaluar pacientes que requieren lentes toricos para corregir el astigmatismo y pacientes con antecedente de cirug&iacute;a LASIK</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">I